```{python}
#| include: false
import jax
import numpy as np
import jax.numpy as jnp
```

## JAX performance (GPU)

::: {.small}
```{python}
key = jax.random.PRNGKey(1234)
x_jnp = jax.random.normal(key, (1000,1000))
x_np = np.array(x_jnp)
x_jnp.device
```
:::

::: {.small}
```{python}
%timeit y = x_np @ x_np
```

```{python}
%timeit y = x_jnp @ x_jnp
```
:::

. . .

::: {.small}
```{python}
%timeit y = 3*x_np + x_np
```
```{python}
%timeit y = 3*x_jnp + x_jnp
```
:::
